These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-1::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, iced-tea, lemonade, milk, soy-milk
House: palace, townhouse, craftsman, modern, colonial, cape-cod
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the colonial house##1
2. the modern house is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the townhouse house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1
6. the modern house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the colonial house is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5     |    6    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | coffee  | iced-tea    | lemonade  | cola      | milk    |
| House      | townhouse  | cape-cod | colonial | palace | modern | craftsman |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-2::.
The people grow 6 different varities of flowers: aconite, tulip, amaryllis, begonia, daffodil, iris
6 different pets are kept: dog, goat, goldfish, guinea-pig, lizard, mouse
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
6. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
7. the person who growsiris is the owner of the mouse##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person who growstulip##1
9. the person who growsaconite is the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3     |   4    |     5      |   6    |
| Flower   | aconite   | daffodil | tulip | iris | begonia     | amaryllis  |
| Pet           | goldfish | goat    | dog      | mouse  | guinea-pig | lizard |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-3::.
6 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, montecristo, chaman, bluemaster, old-henry, fonseca
There are 6 different nationalities: argentine, british, chinese, colombian, german, polish
1. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the fonseca-smoker##1
2. the colombian is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
3. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the bluemaster-smoker##1
4. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the german##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the polish##1
6. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the british##1
7. the colombian is on the far right##1
8. the chinese is the bluemaster-smoker##1
9. the chaman-smoker is the colombian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4     |   5    |     6     |
| Cigar   | bluemaster   | fonseca   | old-henry      | montecristo | swisher  | chaman   |
| Nationality   | chinese | polish | argentine | british   | german | colombian |

