.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: basketball, soccer, swimming, handball, golf, baseball
The people use 6 different means of transport: airplane, bike, helicopter, ship, snowmobile, taxi
1. the person driving the airplane is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
5. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is handball##1
6. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
7. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2   |     3      |     4      |   5   |    6    |
| Sport   | swimming  | handball | basketball      | soccer  | baseball | golf |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi  | snowmobile | helicopter | ship  | bike    |

