7. the american is on the far right##1
8. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
9. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |    5    |    6     |
| City   | marseilles    | liverpool    | berlin | colone     | venice   | hamburg     |
| Nationality   | german | australian | mexican | brazilian | chinese | american |

