.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-9::.
6 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, domino, whist, canasta, billiard
The people use 6 different means of transport: bike, bus, ship, snowmobile, subway, van
1. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing billiard##1
2. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the van is the person playing mah-jongg##1
5. the person playing whist is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
6. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person playing mah-jongg##1
7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
8. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
9. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |    3     |   4    |       5       |     6      |
| Game    | canasta | bridge | whist | billiard    | mah-jongg | domino      |
| Transport   | ship   | bike     | bus      | subway | van           | snowmobile |

