.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-1-10::.
The people use 6 different means of transport: car, quad-bike, subway, snowmobile, skateboard, tram
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: family, mystery, satire, thriller, western, zombie
1. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the person driving the car is on the far right##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is the person driving the quad-bike##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
7. the person driving the tram is the person watching family movies##1
8. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person watching satire movies##1
9. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |   3    |    4    |   5    |    6     |
| Transport          | quad-bike | tram   | skateboard  | subway    | snowmobile  | car |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | family | zombie | western | satire | thriller |

