4. the doctor is the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the fisherman is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the fisherman##1
7. the nurse is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
9. the writer is the person who's birthday is in april##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |       3        |     4     |     5     |   6    |
| Job         | nurse | fisherman | police-officer | paramedic | doctor    | writer |
| Birthday   | december   | july      | september        | may    | august | april  |

